    "en": {
      "title": "The broken machine in Norochchole is back to the national system",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Electricity Board says that the first generator that was disabled at the Norochchola coal plant has been re-connected to the national system. This machine was disabled due to a technical error on the last 10 days.",
        "Thus, the Ceylon Electricity Board had to increase the daily power cut to three hours. Due to the connection of the first generator to the national system, a capacity of 270 MW will be added to the system."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Norochchole",
          "label": "PERSON"
        }
      ],
